| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3910 — Recovery Inhibition (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1b732a6c-93b5-5a5f-a5a2-a4b8c8da1907"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
